## Update intervention


### Resource

`<%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions/:id`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------
id | Intervention ID | yes


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`PATCH, PUT`


### HTTP headers

<%= partial 'includes/http/headers/auth' %>

> HTTP example request

```http
PATCH <%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions/1
```

```http
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
access-token: xxxyyyzzz
token-type: Bearer
client: xxxyyyzzz
uid: user@<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>
```

```json
{
	"intervention": {
		"name": "Intervention updated example 1",
     "status": "published"
	}
}
```

### Note

Possible keys:

 * `name`;
 * `status_event`.

 `status_event` key has to contains one of the following values:

 * `broadcast`;
 * `close`;
 * `to_archive`.


> HTTP response 200 OK

> HTTP response body

```json
{
	"intervention": {
		"name": "Intervention updated example 1",
		"status": "published",
		"interventions": []
	}
}
```
